post.title: Band-A-Rama scheduled for Wednesday, May 21 at 7PM
post.description: Come see the final band performance for the 2013-2014 season. All bands will be performing in the Hi
post.content: Come see the final band performance for the 2013-2014 season. All bands will be performing in the High School Gym. The performance will be recorded should you wish to keep a musical memento of the season. The bands will also be honoring the men and women of our armed services with a special medley of songs, so make sure to invite any family and friends that have served our country so they can be recognized and honored.
